          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Presidential Pardon Transparency Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill requires certain information about presidential pardons and reprieves to be made public.</p> <p>Specifically, the President must publish the issue date, recipient, and full text of each pardon or reprieve granted.</p>]]></text>
          <updateDate>2019-02-25T05:00:00Z</updateDate>
          <name>Introduced in House</name>
        </item>
